		<article class="item-blog col-md-4 post-4081 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-alcuin-news category-authors category-awards" id="post-4081">	

        	<div class="post-container">

			



<div class="post-name">

	<h2 class="entry-title">

		<a href="http://alcuinsociety.com/robert-bringhurst-recipient-of-reid-award-and-medal/" title="Robert Bringhurst recipient of Reid Award and Medal"> Robert Bringhurst recipient of Reid Award and Medal</a>

	</h2>

    <div class="entry-meta entry-header">
	<span class="published">December 9, 2018 by Lynn Copeland</span>
	<span class="meta-sep"> / </span>
	<span class="comment-count"><span>Comments Off<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Robert Bringhurst recipient of Reid Award and Medal</span></span></span>
    
    </div>
</div>



<div class="entry-content">

    <p><img class="size-medium wp-image-4085 alignright" src="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Robert-Bringhurst-3-186x300.jpg" alt="" width="186" height="300" srcset="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Robert-Bringhurst-3-186x300.jpg 186w, http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Robert-Bringhurst-3.jpg 372w" sizes="(max-width: 186px) 100vw, 186px" />The typographer, book designer and author Robert Bringhurst has been awarded the tenth Robert R. Reid Award and Medal for lifetime achievement in the book arts in Canada by the Alcuin Society. The Medal will be presented in Vancouver on a date to be announced.</p>
<p>Awarded the Order of Canada in 2013, Bringhurst is renowned for his seminal work, <em>The Elements of Typographic </em><em>Style </em>described as “the finest book ever written about typography”<a href="#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1">[1]</a>, which has been issued in three editions.</p>
<p>Through his close friendship with Haida artist Bill Reid, Bringhurst has studied and published extensively on Haida art and myths, including three volumes of translations of Haida myths with the collective title <em>Mas</em><em>terworks o</em><em>f the Classical Haida Mythtellers </em>and his work on Haida oral poetry, <em>A Story as Sharp as a Knife</em>. Although the Haida work was subject to some controversy, “most academic discussion and recognition… was positive”<a href="#_ftn2" name="_ftnref2">[2]</a>. Bringhurst has published twenty volumes of poetry, and fifteen volumes of prose. Bringhurst is also an award-winning  book designer, for example with his translation of the ancient Greek poet Parmenides involving the creation of a typeface, digital and in metal, based on ancient Greek letters. His <em>The Surface of Meaning: Books and Book Design in Canada, </em>awarded first prize for illustrated prose in the Alcuin Society’s 2008 book design competition, provided a national survey of book design.</p>
<p>Bringhurst has won numerous awards, including the Edward Sapir Prize (Society for Linguistic Anthropology), 2004, and the BC Lieutenant Governor’s Award for Literary Excellence in 2005,  and has received several honorary degrees. It is a great honour for the Alcuin Society to recognize his achievements through the awarding of the Robert R. Reid Award and Medal in 2018.</p>
<p><a href="#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1">[1]</a> <a href="https://www.typography.com/faq/question.php?faqID=60">&#8220;Frequently Asked Questions&#8221;.</a> Hoefler &amp; Frere-Jones<em>. </em>Retrieved December 9, 2018.</p>
<p><a href="#_ftnref2" name="_ftn2">[2]</a> Wikipedia <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Bringhurst">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Bringhurst</a>. Retrieved December 9, 2018.</p>
<p><img class="wp-image-4082 alignnone" src="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/9780974971407-us-300-202x300.jpg" alt="" width="157" height="233" srcset="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/9780974971407-us-300-202x300.jpg 202w, http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/9780974971407-us-300.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 157px) 100vw, 157px" /></p>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-4084 alignnone" src="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/0881792055.jpg" alt="" width="116" height="200" /></p>
<p><img class="wp-image-4083 alignnone" src="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/9780888946072-us-300-245x300.jpg" alt="" width="149" height="182" srcset="http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/9780888946072-us-300-245x300.jpg 245w, http://alcuinsociety.com/content/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/9780888946072-us-300.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 149px) 100vw, 149px" /></p>

</div>







            </div>

		</article>

                

		
                

		
                

        
                

